msgstr "You did...?"

msgctxt "212_Tanimura"
msgid "(This report is missing something... just like Katsuragi said. According to him, he should be the one listed as the killer. But all that's here is the part Saejima played.)"
msgstr "(This report is missing something... just like Katsuragi said. According to him, he should be the one listed as the killer. But all that's here is the part Saejima played.)"

msgctxt "248_Tanimura"
msgid "(Dad... and Sugiuchi? They worked the case together?)"
msgstr "(Dad... and Sugiuchi? They worked the case together?)"

msgctxt "260_Tanimura"
msgid "(Why haven't I heard this before? What the hell's going on?)"
msgstr "(Why haven't I heard this before? What the hell's going on?)"

msgctxt "320_Tanimura"
